{
  "id": "RAW_0da318f1",
  "title": "“封杀”豆包手机助手可以理解，但最终是封不住的",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NjM5MjQ4MQ==&mid=2651779083&idx=1&sn=05ec10e64ec704592e4fc31f97449454",
  "date": "2025-12-08 06:00:00",
  "author": "刘润",
  "siteName": "刘润",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"background-color: inherit; font-size: 1rem;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">最近，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"background-color: inherit; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">朋友圈被豆包手机助手刷屏了。苦等几天</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"background-color: inherit; font-size: 1rem;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">后，我终于拿到了这款有助手技术预览版的手机。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"513\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"504295425\" data-ratio=\"0.88828125\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e8966310&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FEia1pKbzLGbQFy4hQ3fAHoPvkBQpxjMlpaP5O4ahgwmN6zBI4Gq3dVP3yyq73ibicRMRhdTicPoOyg9oXDvDr6CmYQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">赶紧试试到底有多厉害。本来想点个外卖，但考虑到已经有一堆博主测评过，意思不大。我想给它上点强度。我对它说：下午困了，想喝杯咖啡，帮我对比下瑞幸呀、星巴克呀、Manner呀这些牌子，挑个最便宜的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">刚说完，手机就自己动了。看图。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"504295431\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.1958333333333333\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"480\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"480\" data-backh=\"1054\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bad1b91e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FEia1pKbzLGbQFy4hQ3fAHoPvkBQpxjMlp3Ue0b6TYCTxssBNicejPMpmc1WS8vuTsjSedMssLZwtjylYjto3zCJg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">打开美团，找到“外卖”，输入“瑞幸”，记录价格。再输入“星巴克”、“Manner”，对比价格。最后，整理出一堆咖啡的价格，并告诉我哪家店的哪款最便宜。全程1分半，非常丝滑。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">再试一个。给它提个很难做到的要求：帮我找个房子，中山公园附近，预算2000-3500，面积不小于40，一室一户，中间楼层，离地铁站1公里内。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"504295432\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.19375\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"320\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"320\" data-backh=\"702\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7d067669&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FEia1pKbzLGbQFy4hQ3fAHoPvkBQpxjMlpENmwYT5BclD1Bs00ekYRAQOhziaeqwialk0d5ZAVdpPlmicgWkx2FKLDA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">打开“贝壳”，先添加了各种筛选条件。大概两分钟后，打开“携程”看起了民宿。接着还用浏览器搜了起来。最后，做了个总结，先告诉我没找到符合我要求的房子，又解释为什么。不知道有没有心里强忍着骂“这点预算在上海还想租一室一厅，做梦呢”。总之，全程不到6分钟。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-style:normal;\">整个过程，我只做了一件事：动动嘴皮子提出需求。剩下的，全是眼看着手机助手把活儿干完。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">其实，之前我也体验过一些手机厂商类似模式的样机，但效果都不是特别理想。豆包这次的这个技术完成度，确实蛮惊艳的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当然，也有些功能我没体验上。比如，这些天你也许看到了一些新闻，微信、淘宝等一系列APP，宣布在不同程度上“封杀”这款手机。随后，豆包手机助手下线了对微信、淘宝等应用的操作能力。微信也取消了对这款机型的封禁。其实，只要是真“人”在使用，就不应该限制。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这些天，也有很多朋友问我，怎么看这件事？豆包手机助手会怎样改变我们的商业世界？封禁之后会怎样？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">分享我的一些不成熟的想法，不敢说完全正确，供你参考。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-style:normal;\">一句话总结：大厂“封杀”豆包手机助手，这非常可以理解。但最后，一定是封不住的。因为AI手机助手，很可能是下一个时代的流量入口。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"504288934\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.07222222222222222\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;vertical-align: bottom;height: auto !important;width: 676.875px !important;visibility: visible !important;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"42\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cfe4d7ec&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FEia1pKbzLGbSAianibMeFowN62cp5wgDhNicGDCsrUWB0n6DJJ1IwJrfic41DibwSvf1IKodyibxx1HtT5ZPOYvb9SO7w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%26tp%3Dwebp%23imgIndex%3D4\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">01</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 24px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:24px;\">AI手机助手，可能从根基上动摇一批靠</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:24px;\">“</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:24px;\">懒惰税</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:24px;\">”</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:24px;\">的品牌</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-style:normal;\">长期来看，豆包手机助手这种形式（以下我们暂且叫它“AI手机助手”），会对商业世界产生一个不小的影响：从根本上动摇品牌的“懒惰税”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">懒惰税，听起来有点费解，但这不是一个新概念。举个例子，把时间倒推20年，在没有互联网的时代。你在家门口的小卖部买酱油，5块钱一瓶。其实，马路对面那家超市只要4块5。但这30米的距离，你要过红绿灯，要躲避车流，太麻烦。于是你想：算了，就这买吧。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-style:normal;\">家门口小卖部多赚的那5毛钱，就是你的“懒惰税”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">后来，互联网出现了。淘宝们把全国的商品都摆在你面前。鼠标一点，价格从高到低排序，没有一丁点模糊空间。互联网，就这样干掉了一大批赚“懒惰税”的线下商家。当然，淘宝们也因此被骂了很多年，“搞死线下经济”的大帽子，从没摘下来过。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-style:normal;\">但是，互联网只是抹平了“渠道懒惰税”，“品牌懒惰税”依然存在。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">什么是品牌懒惰税？再举个例子。瑞幸卖9块9的咖啡，你上瘾了、习惯了、进入你的心智了。基本就再也不会费力去找更便宜的咖啡了。哪怕隔壁的库迪砸广告疯狂大喊：我8块8！我8块8！你听见了吗？我8块8！你都可能心想，算了，就这一块钱，还得下个新APP、注册账号、绑定手机、还要深受尝试新品牌可能带来的口味“惊吓”...太累了。瑞幸9块9，挺好。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-style:normal;\">你看，因为习惯了一个品牌而“懒得换”，这就是新时代的“品牌懒惰税”。所谓的品牌忠诚，很多时候并不是真的好到无可替代，而仅仅是“懒得换”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但是，AI手机助手的这种形式，将像互联网击溃渠道懒惰税一样。击溃一大批品牌懒惰税。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">原因很简单，AI没有惯性，没有情感，更不怕麻烦。你对手机说：“我要一杯最便宜的冰美式”。根本不用你费脑子，哪怕只有1毛钱的差价，AI都能瞬间抓取。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它的行动逻辑，很可能是这样：周一，瑞幸发了9.9元券，它买瑞幸。周二，库迪搞8.8元大促，它买库迪。周三，又有不知道哪个新品牌弄了7块7，那就买它。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-style:normal;\">换句话说，极端情况下，再也没有什么“获客-留存-转化”了。每一次购买，都是一次新的获客。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"504288934\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.07222222222222222\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;vertical-align: bottom;height: auto !important;width: 676.875px !important;visibility: visible !important;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"42\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cfe4d7ec&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FEia1pKbzLGbSAianibMeFowN62cp5wgDhNicGDCsrUWB0n6DJJ1IwJrfic41DibwSvf1IKodyibxx1HtT5ZPOYvb9SO7w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%26tp%3Dwebp%23imgIndex%3D4\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">02</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 24px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:24px;\">未来，手机可能变成流量分发入口</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-style:normal;\">看懂了这些，你就能理解，为什么这么多大厂，都要或多或少“封杀”AI手机助手。因为这会从根本上动摇他们“流量入口”的商业模式。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">现代互联网平台的商业模式，几乎全部建立在“流量入口”逻辑上。你点进美团搜“盖浇饭”，附近有20家盖浇饭，谁排在前面？那就是美团说了算了。你上淘宝搜“吹风机”，全网2000家大小吹风机供应商，谁排在前面？那就是淘宝说了算了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">占据流量入口，将流量分发给各家供应商。然后，平台才能或者抽佣、或者广告服务。总之，这是他们商业模式的根基和起点。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-style:normal;\">然而，AI手机助手的出现，似乎让人们看到了新时代的流量入口。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">想想看这个场景，你对手机说一声“今天中午帮我点盖浇饭，最好是青椒肉丝的，加点咸菜和鸡蛋”。会发生什么？它会自动选择平台、对比商家、帮你配餐。你只需要在最后付钱的那个环节“确认”一下，就可以等着开饭了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">看起来没什么大不了？其实，这个影响很大。不仅选商家的操作由AI代劳，连“是不是用美团”点单，都是AI说了算了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">这个逻辑一旦成</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">熟，商业世界可能就完全不一样了。这些APP，将全部成为被调用的“供应商”。AI手机助手，成为</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">了那个唯一的流量入口。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">天知道到时候，会不会像今天给平台投流竞价排名一样，各大平台轮番给AI手机竞价排名？你想，这简直是在断互联网大厂们的根。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这就是为什么我说，大厂封杀AI手机助手，这非常可以理解。没有人愿意仅仅“被调用”。没有人愿意从“地主”变成“长工”。没有人愿意成为下个时代的“供应商”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然而，封禁会有用吗？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">我得说，没用。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"504288934\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.07222222222222222\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;vertical-align: bottom;height: auto !important;width: 676.875px !important;visibility: visible !important;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"42\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cfe4d7ec&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FEia1pKbzLGbSAianibMeFowN62cp5wgDhNicGDCsrUWB0n6DJJ1IwJrfic41DibwSvf1IKodyibxx1HtT5ZPOYvb9SO7w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%26tp%3Dwebp%23imgIndex%3D4\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">03</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 24px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:24px;\">只要消费者获益，趋势就无法阻挡</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">商业的发展，从来不遵循巨头的意志。只由一批人决定：消费者。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">商业历史无数次告诉我们：和“消费者受益”作斗争，是真正的“螳臂当车”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">你说，这种“语音操作AI手机干活”的形式，比起你拿个手机戳戳戳点半天，是不是体验更好了？当然，只要你使用过，我敢说，这是显而易见的更好。大概和智能手机对比翻盖手机一样。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">既然这样，那就完事了。对于AI手机助手来说，你想封？那就请封吧。美团不接受，流量就给淘宝闪购。淘宝不接受，流量就给京东得物小红书。携程不接受，流量就给同程飞猪。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">甚至，如果这些老平台们真的联合起来抵制，那也问题不大。反正只要消费者愿意用，有的是年轻人，在排队等着创业做新时代的平台。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">商业，从来只看一件事：消费者究竟是不是受益了？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">所以，未来一定会来。只不过，如果让我们畅想一下，也许不是以这次豆包手机助手的“GUI Agent”形式。而是以一种类似“API Agent”的方式，更加丝滑的进行。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">乍一听有点费解。简单解释一下。这次豆包手机助手的技术模式，叫GUI Agent。GUI的意思，是“图形用户界面”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">用大白话说，GUI Agent，是在“模拟人的手指操作手机”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">举个例子，你看这段截屏。我在让它找房子的时候，给了它一个租金范围“2000元-3500元”。它上来就先拉到2300，多了，又往回拉到1800，少了。再拉，终于对了。右边也差不多，反复几次，拉到3600，实在拉不准了，就这样差不多了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它就像一个不太会用手机的老人，眯着眼，小心翼翼地在屏幕上滑来滑去，起码要花上两分钟。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"504295434\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.571875\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"331\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c29ad3b8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FEia1pKbzLGbQFy4hQ3fAHoPvkBQpxjMlpRmTsz88dLbjcFEEo1M0q2yhl5sAj68DCloTeC4ocmpPddl6yiaUPStQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">原因很简单，它的操作权限，只能模拟你的手指拉拉拉点点点。没办法直接进入贝壳后台，把那个数字调到2000元。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">那，有没有更好的解决方案呢？有，这就是“API Agent”。API的意思，是“程序编程接口”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">API级权限，就是和微信、美团、淘宝、贝壳、携程们达成合作，拿到他们后台的接口，直接在APP后台操作。你在屏幕上看不到任何演示，但在后台手机已经帮你完成了所有操作。数据就像瞬移一样，精准归位。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">如果说GUI是在模拟人类的手指，那API就是联通了APP的大脑。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">只不过，很明显，这不是豆包一家可以完成的工作。它需要淘宝、美团、微信等千千万万个APP开发者们，把自己的后台打开，和AI手机助手实现数据层面的打通。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当然，咱们看看过往的流量入口变迁，其实没有一次是容易的。这个过程里会有不少困难和阻碍。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">比如，利润如何分成？当年滴滴这样的打车平台问世时，也曾引起不小的争议。你就写两行代码，弄个平台，就要分走我白花花的营业额？这真的合理吗？直到今天，这种争议都没有停止。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">比如，信息安全如何保护？想当年支付宝刚刚问世的时候，也曾经面对铺天盖地的质疑。我的天呐，我的钱都经过你付出去，这还得了？我怎么知道你会不会卷着钱跑路了？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">新事物的出现，总是伴随着争议。现在的AI手机，也面临同样的局面。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">相信你最近一定看到过不少质疑，有人担心隐私泄露，有人担心它破坏了APP生态规则。这些担心都很对。毕竟，要把手机全权交给AI，这背后的信任成本高得吓人。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然而如果你问我，我还是很坚定的相信，发展的问题，要靠发展来解决。就像汽车刚发明的时候，没有红绿灯，也没有安全带，确实容易出事。但最终的方案，并不是回去坐马车，而是发明了红绿灯、斑马线、安全气囊。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">然而，那句话，趋势，是没有办法阻挡的。就像今天滴滴和支付宝已经嵌入生活方方面面一样。这次的AI手机，最后也一定会形成一套新时代的方案。只不过这个方案究竟如何，也许就不是我们现在能想象的了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">看到这儿，你可能就理解了，为什么豆包团队在售卖页面非常醒目地写着一句提示：此次发售的“豆包手机”为工程机，并不适用于普通消费者。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"504295433\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.5156912637828668\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1179\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"876\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=77ee403a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FEia1pKbzLGbQFy4hQ3fAHoPvkBQpxjMlpb4VyN17ZXeIicSGHricrFYqvZz63pzZZWWX43F050MtvdSTPZmDbekDw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">说实话，我很喜欢这个细节。这是一种对消费者非常负责的“预期管理”。丑话说在前面：现在的技术虽然酷炫，但还很有很多不足，是给爱折腾的极客尝鲜的。想买回来就当主力机用的普通用户，先别来。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">从这个角度来看，这次的豆包手机，也许更像是一份“邀请函”。看得清趋势的同行者，共创一个未来。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我确实，很期待那一天早点到来。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 9 []\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 4 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h2&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;4 9 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;font-weight: 400;font-size: 16px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-variant-ligatures: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;text-align: left;caret-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: bold;\">观点</span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"3 3 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h2&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;4 7 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Mic